        {
            "title": "堅尼地城女途人疑棄用過路設施捱貨車撞 半昏迷送院救治",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"女途人捱貨車撞，半昏迷送院。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/6089e8ea953ba00e6330bab5efda6e28/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250301/_2025030111244170584.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">女途人捱貨車撞，半昏迷送院。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>西區發生貨車撞女途人意外。今(1 日)早上9時26分，一部密斗貨車沿士美菲路右轉入科士街，撞倒一名橫過馬路的女途人，經調查後，懷疑事主並無依照過路設施過路，因此被密斗貨車撞倒，她頭、手及肩膊受傷，半清醒被送往瑪麗醫院治理，意外原因有待調查。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111285/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"肇事貨車停在現場。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a1ebb17ac82208cefd5dc645ae0c8ac4/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_105414557.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        肇事貨車停在現場。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111286/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4e49c72784abab554ada5707a025945f/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_105414557_02.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警員到場調查。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111287/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"肇事貨車。楊偉亨攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3b7de62e0e48a499f60872608b62ba5d/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_105414557_04.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        肇事貨車。楊偉亨攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"none-100\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4111288/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"被撞女子半昏迷送院救治。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e286248433ecd2d926c392a543eee291/2025-03/KakaoTalk_20250301_105807345_01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        被撞女子半昏迷送院救治。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
